Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:03:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They landed on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an island with two parts, one \Nburning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After learning about Caesar's motive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they are on the move to save the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kidnap Caesar, and escape from the island--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all while trying to escape Shinokuni.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have treated him\N as my young brother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and watched closely\N over him as he grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard for you, Vergo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I need you to take care of Law there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:04:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna make him wish\N that he was never born.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So kill him in a horrific way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy Dies from Exposure?!\N The Spine-chilling Snow Woman Monet!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:44.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}D BUILDING - THE "SAD" MANUFACTURING ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like my hand has been bitten
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by my own dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even for a mischievous child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were too smart\N for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tend to die young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be easiest for me to kill \Nyou by crushing your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not gonna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll torment you slowly as I please
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and warp your smart-ass face...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:32.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}C BUILDING 4TH FLOOR - CAESAR'S RESEARCH ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What does she want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bird woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go after the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing again! But it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these walls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bird woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten-layer Kamakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are ten layers to this Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy to break the snow walls
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if they're layered one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you trying to buy time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can break them all quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you can break this Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, stop wasting my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm gonna lose you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I will win\N if I fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the strongest isn't always\N the winner in a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a block of ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't push me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're now in my embrace
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your power is diminished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will lose all of\N your physical strength
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to my cold body in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your heart will freeze
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you will
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,die in your sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's snowing heavily around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel very tired, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.18,0:10:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just the beginning\N of the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jet Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What tremendous hidden strength he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But falling through here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will land him in the slide to the \Ngarbage dump deep underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll never be able to come \Nback up unless he can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:11:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect him to\N sabotage himself like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:29.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}B BUILDING 3RD FLOOR - NEAR THE BISCUIT ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must never\N eat that candy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard\N but you have to endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you pass through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go to the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:11:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in our way,\N you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop them without hurting them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effect of the Rumble Ball\N is about to wear off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can eat the candy soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! To the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can eat the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kids, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take more of the drug,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will ruin your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't save them\N because I have no power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Chopper-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with those kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've gotten more violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us what's going on, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar is trying to turn them into giants
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to make them demonic \Nsoldiers, just as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't handle them alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:14:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have to stop them\N as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Biscuit Room is to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candies are there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha is the only child in her \Nright mind and she's helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were trying to stop the other children
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is protecting the candies\N in the room all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here at the Biscuit Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mil Fleurs
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gigantesco Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward while I hold them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not gonna be\N stopped so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll stop at nothing\N when they're in that state!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:15:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.20,0:15:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's evil candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We asked Chopper-chan and\N the others to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't listen to them,\N we can't go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! That's no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna eat it all yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let them have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:16:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home with everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold! I'm freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The exit is sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.34,0:16:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to\N worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Monet-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the bird woman\N that I told you about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet-san, please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha, it's not nice\N to keep it all to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to share\N the candies with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.57,0:16:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she uses sorcery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a Logia-type?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:17:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's our enemy, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monet-san, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:14.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}B BUILDING 2ND FLOOR - AN EXAMINATION ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, where did the boy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He entered into the "secret room"\N where no one is allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and transformed into a small dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy named Momonosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brat who transformed into a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, "the boy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know\N about that, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching it secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened in the "secret room"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got here on the same ship \Nwith him so I've been worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This laboratory is big and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:17:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are various treatment rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's just in a different room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he eating something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't he eat anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, he's eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone about him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the "secret room." Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe one of the\N children knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to let the Master know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd come to this secret room myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the only place I can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all their fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could've been a great show - \Neverything perfect and lovely,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and more befitting of the\N world's greatest scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they screwed it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy G-5!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them regret ruining my plan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even after they go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow down to my scientific prowess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:20:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys frustrated because your \Nscheme is coming crashing down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is that important to you guys, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth, you squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to me, my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Counter Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "What a shame."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.07,0:21:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty sure that I could \Ntake my heart back from Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't expect you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:22:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Vergo-san to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have to be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.66,0:22:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to silence\N you anyway, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better make your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so pleasant to watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a scumbag like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate -
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.37,0:23:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker's rage explodes at the fact \Nthat Vergo's betrayed his men,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.13,0:23:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Vergo closes in on him \Nwith overwhelming Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.49,0:23:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fierce battle between Smoker and Vergo intensifies,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as Smoker puts his spirit and \Npride as a Marine on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fists Collide!\N A Battle of the Two Vice Admirals!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.15,0:23:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
